---
title: Easy Creamy Chorizo Fettuccine with Rocket, Pear & Parmesan Salad
description: Golden strands of fettuccine combine with rich tomato paste, cream and smokey chorizo to create an elegant meal fit for only the
best. Add a sharp rocket and Parmesan salad for crunch and dinner is complete.
